\p \w Te|strong="G5023"\w* phoeiah te, \wj “ \+w Yaak|strong="G0191"\+w* nah \+w hna|strong="G3775"\+w* aka \+w khueh|strong="G2192"\+w* \+w loh|strong="G3588"\+w* \+w ya|strong="G0191"\+w* saeh,” \wj* a \w ti|strong="G3004"\w* nah tih a \w doek|strong="G5455"\w*.   
\s1 Nuettahnah kah a Mangtaeng  
\p
