\v 13 \wj \+w Tedae|strong="G1161"\+w* \+w mangmucoi|strong="G5057"\+w* \+w tah|strong="G3588"\+w* \+w soei|strong="G3113"\+w* \+w pai|strong="G2476"\+w* tih \+w mik|strong="G3788"\+w* \+w pataeng|strong="G3761"\+w* \+w vaan|strong="G3772"\+w* \+w la|strong="G1519"\+w* a \+w dai|strong="G1869"\+w* \+w ngaih|strong="G2309"\+w* \+w pawh|strong="G3756"\+w*. \+w A|strong="G0846"\+w* \+w lungkoe|strong="G4738"\+w* \+w te|strong="G3588"\+w* a \+w tum|strong="G5180"\+w* tih\wj*, '\wj \+w Pathen|strong="G2316"\+w* \+w aw|strong="G3588"\+w*, \+w ka|strong="G3427"\+w* \+w tholh|strong="G0268"\+w* \+w he|strong="G3588"\+w* han \+w dawth|strong="G2433"\+w* lah\wj*,’ \wj a \+w ti|strong="G3004"\+w*\wj*.   
\p
\v 14 \x - \xo 18.14 \xt Mat 23. 12; Luk 14. 11.\x*\wj \+w Nangmih|strong="G5213"\+w* taengah ka \+w thui|strong="G3004"\+w*, \+w anih|strong="G3778"\+w* he \+w pakhat|strong="G1565"\+w* \+w lakah|strong="G3844"\+w* aka \+w tang|strong="G1344"\+w* ngai la \+w a|strong="G0846"\+w* \+w im|strong="G3624"\+w* \+w te|strong="G1519"\+w* a \+w paan|strong="G2597"\+w*. Te \+w dongah|strong="G3754"\+w* \+w amah neh amah|strong="G1438"\+w* aka \+w pomsang|strong="G5312"\+w* \+w boeih|strong="G3956"\+w* \+w tah|strong="G3588"\+w* a \+w tlarhoel|strong="G5013"\+w* sak ni. \+w Tedae|strong="G1161"\+w* \+w amah neh amah|strong="G1438"\+w* aka \+w yalh|strong="G5013"\+w* \+w tah|strong="G3588"\+w* a \+w pomsang|strong="G5312"\+w* ni,” \wj* a \w ti|strong="G2036"\w* nah.   
\s1 Camoe a Uem  
\p
\v 15 Te \w vaengah|strong="G1161"\w* \w cahni|strong="G1025"\w* rhoek \w te|strong="G0846"\w* \w taek|strong="G0680"\w* \w van|strong="G2532"\w* saeh \w tila|strong="G2443"\w* \w amah|strong="G0846"\w* taengla a \w bawnhlak|strong="G4374"\w* uh. \w Tedae|strong="G1161"\w* \w hnukbang|strong="G3101"\w* rhoek \w loh|strong="G3588"\w* a \w hmuh|strong="G3708"\w* vaengah \w amih|strong="G0846"\w* te a \w tlung|strong="G2008"\w* uh.  
\v 16 \w Tedae|strong="G1161"\w* \w Jesuh|strong="G2424"\w* \w loh|strong="G3588"\w* \w amih|strong="G0846"\w* a \w khue|strong="G4341"\w* tih, “\w Camoe|strong="G3813"\w* rhoek \w te|strong="G3588"\w* \w kamah|strong="G3165"\w* \w taengla|strong="G4314"\w* ha \w pawk|strong="G2064"\w* ham han \w hlah|strong="G0863"\w* uh, \w amih|strong="G0846"\w* te \w kang|strong="G2967"\w* uh \w boeh|strong="G3361"\w*. \w Amih|strong="G5108"\w* \w ham|strong="G3588"\w* ni \w Pathen|strong="G2316"\w* kah \w ram|strong="G0932"\w* a \w om|strong="G2076"\w*.  
